WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to exploring the ancient Kingdom of Wadai

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The Kingdom of Wadai, one of the most important Islamic kingdoms in Central Africa

3
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Founded in the 17th century by Sultan Abd al-Karim

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
The kingdom flourished for over three centuries

5
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Located in what is now eastern Chad

6
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
The first capital was the historic city of Wara

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Later the capital moved to the city of Abéché

8
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
A rich cultural heritage worth preserving and exploring 